reviewText:
Customer service was great, fast shipping.......
Now this is my opinion...... the movie it's self although entertaining was not like the book.
So if you have read the book series do your best to forget you know anything about the books, and you will be fine , and not be yelling at your TV.  lol
Product arrived on time and was exactly as described.
Grandchildren love it and now want a baby dragon.
Even though it does not fallow the book it is still a good movie as a stand alone product
